Melchana: Finally...

She landed the ship and lowered the door.

Melchana: Alright now, I'm Melchana, Tripredacus War Trainer. I am 
here to accompany the Autobot Ambassador to the Shadow Destiny... And 
I wish to speak with Gesper. Can you tell him to get his butt over 
here?
